# Netlify Redirects

# Explicitly handle sitemap files
/sitemap.xml    /sitemap.xml   200
/sitemap.html   /sitemap.html  200
/sitemap.txt    /sitemap.txt   200

# Fallback: Redirect sitemap.xml to alternative formats if there are issues
/sitemap.xml    /sitemap.html  404
/sitemap.xml    /sitemap.txt   404

